<div id="main_content">
	<h2>'Slow Ride' Rock Hit Describes Economic Recovery</h2>
	
	<p class="article_info">
		
			By Christine Dellert
		
		<span class="date">Sept. 30, 2010</span></p>
	
	
	
		<div class="article_img" style="width: 345px;">

			<img alt="Article Main Picture" src="../resources/sites/UCF/content/live/NEWS/2000/NE2279/en_US/foghatmain.jpg" height="226" width="345"  /> 
			
			<p>Foghat released its 1975 album "Fool for the City" with the classic hit song, "Slow Ride." </p>
			
				<p class="note"><a class="full_photo" id="popup.jsp?article_id=0024004107a42ec8a012b4426d5b300755b">Full Photo</a></p>
			
			
			
			
					
						
						
						
					
			
			
			
					
						
						
						
					
			
			
			
		</div>
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
		
			<div id="related">
				<h3>Related Contacts and Links:</h3>
				<ul>
		
